RootTable.Filter: SELECT c.name as 'Connector Name', o.name as 'Obj Name', o.stereotype as 'Obj Stereotype', o.status as 'Obj Status', startPort.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, startPort.object_type as CLASSTYPE, startPort.name as 'Start Port Name', endPort.name as 'End Port Name' FROM t_object o , t_xref xflow , t_connector cflow , t_xref x , t_connector c, t_object startPort, t_object endPort WHERE o.status Like '<Search Term>' AND o.stereotype = 'CSUMessage' AND o.ea_guid in (substring(xflow.description,0,39),substring(xflow.description,39,39), substring(xflow.description,78,39),substring(xflow.description,117,39),substring(xflow.description,156,39), substring(xflow.description,195,39),substring(xflow.description,234,39),substring(xflow.description,273,39), substring(xflow.description,312,39),substring(xflow.description,351,39)) AND xflow.Behavior = 'conveyed' AND cflow.ea_guid = xflow.client AND cflow.ea_guid in (substring(x.description,0,39),substring(x.description,39,39), substring(x.description,78,39),substring(x.description,117,39),substring(x.description,156,39), substring(x.description,195,39),substring(x.description,234,39),substring(x.description,273,39), substring(x.description,312,39),substring(x.description,351,39)) AND x.Behavior = 'abstraction' AND c.ea_guid = x.client AND startPort.object_id = c.start_object_id AND endPort.object_id = c.end_object_id
